{"tid":1746564,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[公投] 究竟痴文宣應該black bloc 定街坊look?","createTime":"2019-11-22T19:52:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T06:50:43.000Z","uid":139316,"like":66,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"35fd4c5a675e5e20339e4bfb7418680ef4c196e7","tid":1746564,"uid":139316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T19:52:04.000Z","msg":"點解咁問呢，就係因為我覺得痴文宣如果full black bloc，姐係由頭黑到落尾，眼耳都遮埋會好礙眼。一黎可能嚇親街坊，驚動保安，二黎仲可能有藍絲報警，俾狗見到成身black bloc 一定有排搞。相反如果街坊裝，eg 帶頂帽同口罩，咁就冇咁礙眼，啲人都可能由你貼，有狗嚟到可能見你咁街坊，你又好聲好氣，都廢是搞你，始終都只係貼下文宣 (except d 文宣串9啲狗啦) <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/amp.lihkg.com/thread/1306732/page/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Famp.lihkg.com%2Fthread%2F1306732%2Fpage%2F1&d=ZU5rKlsKhNp37FgV%2FTwvgt%2FmPfBwacFXLzUp2rw9Z8Q%3D&h=d1a4cd9b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/amp.lihkg.com/thread/1306732/page/1</a><br />\n呢個po 就話捉到入到罪就罰1500，如果係既，咁full black bloc 仲有機會瀨屎上身，eg非法集結。<br />\n<br />\n大家點睇？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 街坊裝都ok<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一定要full black bloc"},{"pid":"52bd0d445e7b57bbb9812c2fed4529e064eceab1","tid":1746564,"uid":137721,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T19:52:57.000Z","msg":"風褸+彩虹戰衣<br />\n<br />\n3秒變身"},{"pid":"1bb3c3e2832be5f2d5bd0f486bf87eb749bc23c0","tid":1746564,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T19:54:32.000Z","msg":"全黑係為左掩飾身份<br />\n等曱甴追蹤唔到你<br />\n或者上到庭話曱甴有機會認錯人 所以判冇罪"},{"pid":"9dd57356685243ab6a62b3474ef23aa4580f7325","tid":1746564,"uid":108571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T19:57:32.000Z","msg":"街坊<br />\nBtw 正負皮維護中"},{"pid":"bf6db9bdf5799590d5774544809ea1d3dfbd9f4d","tid":1746564,"uid":73293,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T20:29:23.000Z","msg"